ntent":"Optionally, select or clear <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Sync updated files back to the local folder when I eject the SD card<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>."},{"content":"This option is enabled by default.","pos":[30978,31012]},{"content":"When this option is enabled, files are synced from the emulator back to the folder on the development computer when you eject the SD card.","pos":[31013,31151]},{"pos":[31157,31179],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Eject the SD card<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>."},{"content":"Click <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Eject SD card<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>.","pos":[31185,31209]},{"content":"When you eject the SD card, the following things happen:","pos":[31210,31266]},{"pos":[31276,31399],"content":"if you have selected <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Sync updated files back to the local folder when I eject the SD card<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>, the following things happen:"},{"content":"The files on the simulated SD card on the emulator are copied to the specified folder on the development computer.","pos":[31412,31526]},{"content":"A progress bar indicates the progress of the sync operation.","pos":[31527,31587]},{"pos":[31600,31656],"content":"The <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Eject SD card<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> button changes to <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Cancel sync<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept>."},{"pos":[31669,31812],"content":"If you click <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Cancel sync<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> while the sync operation is in progress, the card is ejected and the results of the sync operation are incomplete."},{"pos":[31821,31885],"content":"The <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Eject SD card<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> button changes back to <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Insert SD card<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept>."},{"pos":[31889,32000],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Note<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>  Since an SD card used by the phone is formatted with the FAT32 file system, 32GB is the maximum size."},{"content":"The speed of reading from and writing to the simulated SD card is throttled to imitate real